{
  "stem": "9730.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when they would come to a Jewish house, they would sing their, their hate songs to the effect-- one, one of them I remember-- when Jewish blood splatters from our knives, then things will go twice as well.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was one of their famous songs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they would always time it so that they would sing those stanzas when they were marching by a Jewish home.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Or ?], I remember, for instance, in the early time after Hitler's assumption of power, my religious school teacher, by that time one in Heidelberg, saying to the class of Jewish students, well, we have witnessed a great upheaval recent, in recent times within Germany.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We saw it coming but were unable to stop it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "For the time being, all we can do is hope that nobody comes to our doorstep and slits our throats.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was, of course, a, a great disillusionment for me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and you sort of made the best of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It meant that I, I would spend a great deal more time at home, not associating with anybody because I was physically removed from many of my friends in, in Heidelberg.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I would do what was still possible.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, books were always-- it was always possible to read.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Radio, in those days, we could still listen to.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Only later, that was prohibited.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, and so I would concentrate on things like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, by '35, roughly, it, it had become evident that we better start the ball rolling and, and try to do something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That meant, of course, that the younger members of our family would leave first.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And since my sister was at, at the right stage of her training, she, she made the first attempt to leave.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
